{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-template-book-js","path":"/books/nature/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>This Nature poetry collection is comprised of thirty-seven metered rhyming poems about nature and the seasons.  </p>\n<p>The nature poetry collection begins with 5 poems that are not season specific. The rest of the collection of nature poems are divided up into seasons.  </p>\n<p>Each collection of poems about a season starts with a title page and a long narrative poem about the specific season. For each season there are seven metered rhyming poems about the nature specific to that season.  </p>\n<p>This book can be bought with cryptocurrency.  </p>\n<p>The book is dedicated to Woden.  </p>","frontmatter":{"date":"January 29, 2016","title":"Nature","download":null,"buy":"what_goes_here","preview1":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/png;base64,","aspectRatio":0.5617977528089888,"src":"/static/f33179b8f431c4d0d975a5733bb89235/3c17d/nature_poetry_cover.png","srcSet":"/static/f33179b8f431c4d0d975a5733bb89235/69585/nature_poetry_cover.png 200w,\n/static/f33179b8f431c4d0d975a5733bb89235/497c6/nature_poetry_cover.png 400w,\n/static/f33179b8f431c4d0d975a5733bb89235/3c17d/nature_poetry_cover.png 720w","sizes":"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px"}}},"preview2":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/png;base64,","aspectRatio":0.5617977528089888,"src":"/static/e7045cf5eb50784b9b4d3831f58476a3/3c17d/nature_poetry_autumn_chapter.png","srcSet":"/static/e7045cf5eb50784b9b4d3831f58476a3/69585/nature_poetry_autumn_chapter.png 200w,\n/static/e7045cf5eb50784b9b4d3831f58476a3/497c6/nature_poetry_autumn_chapter.png 400w,\n/static/e7045cf5eb50784b9b4d3831f58476a3/3c17d/nature_poetry_autumn_chapter.png 720w","sizes":"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px"}}},"preview3":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/png;base64,","aspectRatio":0.5617977528089888,"src":"/static/3caefc0327cf03156a2e82031582ee51/3c17d/nature_poetry_bare_t